&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 1.2;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;sup&gt;PolyAI automates customer service through lifelike voice assistants that let customers lead a conversation. Our voice assistants make it possible for businesses to deliver outstanding customer service that rivals their human agents. Our customers, which include the world’s leading logos, are expanding how they use our platform, driving automation of critical customer service operations and integrating PolyAI into their daily customer service workflows.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 1;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;sub&gt;We&#39;re looking for a &lt;strong&gt;Creative Director&lt;/strong&gt; to lead a full rebrand of PolyAI and establish a creative function that can scale with the company.&lt;/sub&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;sub&gt;This is a rare opportunity: a category-defining AI company at an inflection point, with the resources to do it right. You&#39;ll build from a strong foundation — proven technology, marquee customers, and a product that genuinely changes how enterprises serve their customers — but the visual identity, brand voice, and design system haven&#39;t kept pace with our growth or our ambitions.&lt;/sub&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;sub&gt;You&#39;ll own everything from brand strategy and visual identity to campaign creative and product design language. You&#39;ll hire and manage a distributed creative team, set the creative bar across the company, and act as a strategic partner to Marketing, Product, and Executive leadership.&lt;/sub&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;sub&gt;This role reports to the Head of Brand and sits on the Marketing leadership team.&lt;/sub&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;sub&gt;What You&#39;ll Do:&lt;/sub&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;sub&gt;Brand Overhaul&lt;/sub&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;sub&gt;Lead a comprehensive rebrand of PolyAI — from positioning and visual identity to brand voice, messaging architecture, and design system — fit for a Series D enterprise AI company competing with Salesforce, Genesys, and Five9 in the boardroom&lt;/sub&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;sub&gt;Develop a brand that makes the abstract tangible: helping enterprise buyers (CX leaders, IT executives, CFOs) understand, trust, and feel excited about voice AI&lt;/sub&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;sub&gt;Build and maintain a scalable brand system — guidelines, component libraries, templates — that enables consistency across a fast-moving, globally distributed org&lt;/sub&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li st

&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 1.2;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;sup&gt;PolyAI automates customer service through lifelike voice assistants that let customers lead a conversation. Our voice assistants make it possible for businesses to deliver outstanding customer service that rivals their human agents. Our customers, which include the world’s leading logos, are expanding how they use our platform, driving automation of critical customer service operations and integrating PolyAI into their daily customer service workflows.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 1;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;sub&gt;A &lt;strong&gt;Deployment Strategist&lt;/strong&gt; at PolyAI is the commander in chief of a customer service transformation. It is their job to ensure the success of our real projects, both by managing timelines, overseeing the quality of virtual assistants, and being the point of authority for the client. Day to day, you’ll be listening to real people interacting with our systems, making decisions on how to make them even better, and convincing the client they’re the right ones.&lt;/sub&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 1;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;sub&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Your responsibility will involve:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/sub&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;sub&gt;Own the delivery of transformative virtual assistants at serious scale - from deployments handling hundreds of thousands of calls a day to high-stakes PoCs where your speed, strategy and creativity win the deal&lt;/sub&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;sub&gt;Going beyond individual delivery - advising Fortune 500 customers on how to fundamentally reshape their customer service organisations using gravitas, executive presence and knowledge&lt;/sub&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;sub&gt;Be the single point of accountability for delivery, bridging the gap between client expectations and engineering with clarity&amp;nbsp;&lt;/sub&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;sub&gt;Being the voice of the client, understanding their need, value drivers, sensitivities and values and rallying the rest of the PolyAI team around such needs&lt;/sub&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;sub&gt;Track and report on the metrics that matter - value driven success metrics, utilization, adoption, and account health - with the autonomy to know what&#39;s working and what isn&#39;t and the creativity to bring the right team together to solve it&lt;/sub&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;sub&gt;Communicating wins to clients in a way that builds trust, proves value, and drives expansion&lt;/sub&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&

