&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;sup&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;PolyAI’s go-to-market spans both an enterprise and developer / product-led growth motions. You will be effective across both, with specific focus areas calibrated to your strengths and team priorities.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
